title: PREVIEW: No. 9 Tech, Oklahoma set for first matchup - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: PREVIEW: No. 9 Tech, Oklahoma set for first matchup - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: No. 9 Texas Tech and Oklahoma will square off against each other for the first time this season at 8 p.m. on Wednesday at the Lloyd Noble Center in Norman, Oklahoma.
